defaultThe CIEH welcomes the Select Committee’s Inquiry into the Government’s review of housing standards and its proposals on the Code for Sustainable Homes.  The principal role for Environmental Health Practitioners is in the maintenance of housing standards and conditions in the private rented sector, but there is strong interest in the standards 
defaultet
default for new build housing
default, not least
default as these are of course the private rented dwellings of the future. The consultation also raises important issues about accessibility and space standards
