defaultCIEH position
default&#xa0;
default2.2
default              
defaultThe distinction between mandatory and voluntary is sensible, but the 
defaultbalance between the two has 
defaultto be set carefully. 
defaultT
defaulthe housing market 
defaultcurrently favours the 
default“seller” and voluntary codes cannot be relied on 
defaultalone 
defaultto achieve the housing stock required in the longer term. 
default 
defaultFurthermore, government policies, especially its carbon-reduction targets, depend heavily on the performance of the current and future housing stock. The government should also be planning to ensure that the housing stock is better suited to the demographic shifts that are taking place. 
